      "text": "Un gahje tam Israëlitexu \nWihran pakkat Manku-Rakta/ \nun pahrduhre abbejuß zauri / to \nIsraëlitexu Wihrn / un to See- \nwu/zaur wiꞥſchu Wehderu."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad mittejahs ta Mohzi- \nba no teem Israëta Behrneem/ \ntee nu/ kas tannî Mohzibâ no- \nmirruſchi / bija diwidefmits \ntfchetr tuhkſtoſchi."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad runnaja tas Klungs \nus Mohfu/ un fazztja :"
