      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pineas/Eeleasara Dehls/ \nAärona ta Brestexa Dehla/ irr \nmannu Bahrsibu nowehrſis no \nteem Israëta Behrneem/tapehz/ \nka wiꞥſch mannas Duźnas deht \ndufinojis wiꞥſnu Starpâ / ta/ \nka es tohs Israëta Behrnus neſ- \ntu iſdeldejis mannâ Dufmibaâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ſukki: Reds/ Es \ndohmu wiꞥnam mannu Derri- \nbu ta Meera."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥnam / ar wiꞥna \nDſimmunu pakkat wiꞥnu / \nbuhs ta muhschiga Preestexa- \nAmmata Derriba buht/ tapehz/ \nka wiꞥſch preekſch ſawu Deewu \nbahrgi dufinojis/ un tohs Isra- \nëta Behrnus falihdsinajis irr."
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta nokauta Israëlite- \nWiha Wahrs / kas ar to"
    },
