      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Midijaniteru Seewu nokante \nbij/ bija Simrus/ weens Dehle \nSallus/ weens Wirfneeks / ta \nSiemeaniteru Tehwa Namma"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tahs nokautas Mi- \ndijaniteru Seewas Wahrs bija \nKasbi / weena Meita Zurus/ \nweena Lauschu Wirfneeka/ kah \nda Tehwa Namma ſtarp teem \nMidijanitereem."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KlINGS run- \nnaja us Mohsu/ un fazztja :"
    },
