      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Darrajt teem Midijani- \ntexeem gruhti/ un kanjeet tahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tee irr juns gruht \ndarrijufchi zaur ſaiwahn Wilte \nbahm / ko tee ar Wiltn pret \njuns irr nodohmajſchi / zaur \nPeoru/ un zaur Kasbi to Midi- \njana Wirfneeka Meitu / ſawu \nMahsu/kas nokauta irr tai Moh- \nzibas Deenâ Peora deht."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N tas notiffahs pehz \ntahs Mohzibas / tad \nrunnaja tas KlINGS \nus Mohsu / un us Eeleasaru \nAärona ta Brestexa Dehlu/ ni \nfazztja:"
